TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
Have you heard anything about a cure for the Wailing Death?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병 치료법에 대해 들은 게 있습니까?

TextEng: Did you know anything about the attack on the Academy?
Text: 사관학교 습격에 관해 들은 게 있습니까?

TextEng: How did you end up here tending the afflicted.
Have you heard any rumors lately? You know, gossip and the like?
You know stuff 'bout cure for sick?
What you know 'bout fight at Academy?
Text: 사관학교에서 싸움 난 거, 뭐 알아?

TextEng: You be nurse. How you get your job here?
Text: 너 여기서 병자 돌보는 사람. 어떻게 이 일 하게 됐어?

TextEng: You hear gossip or rumors or stuff?
That's it? You haven't heard the rumors about a cure from Waterdeep?
Text: 그게 다요? 워터딥에서 온 치료법 소문은 못 들었나요?

TextEng: You not hear stuff 'bout cure from Waterdeep?
Text: 워터딥에서 온 치료법 소문 못 들었어?

TextEng: Tell me what you've heard about Desther.
Text: 데스터에 대해 들은 이야기를 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: Tell me what you've heard about Aribeth.
Text: 아리베스에 대해 들은 이야기를 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: Tell me what you've heard about Fenthick.
Text: 펜딕에 대해 들은 이야기를 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: Tell what you hear 'bout Desther.
Tell what you hear 'bout Aribeth.
Tell what you hear 'bout Fenthick.
What were they saying?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You don't like Desther much, do you?
What them say?
Aren't you afraid of contracting the plague yourself?
You not scared you get sick, too?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, telling me won't do any harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 내게 말해도 해가 될 건 없어요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. Will hurt nobody.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 무엇을 알려 주실 수 있습니까?

TextEng: What you know 'bout plague?
I want to ask you something else.
Me have other question.
Can I ask you some directions?
Neverwinter big place. Me need directions.
Text: 네버윈터 큰 곳. 나 길 좀 알려줘.
